languages.text: "Не сейчас. Она должна провести нас в замок — без нее враги заподозрят неладное, а мы раскроем свою осведомленность раньше времени".

traits.locale_text: "Обязательно. Но сначала она приведет нас в логово зверя".

languages.text: "Not now. She needs to accompany us to the castle. Her absence would raise the enemy's suspicions, and the revelation that we know what we know would come too early."

languages.text: 「今はだめです。彼女には私たちと一緒に城へ来てもらう必要があります。彼女がいなければ、敵に疑念を抱かせてしまいます。私たちが何を把握しているかが明るみに出てしまうのは時期尚早です」
languages.original_text: "Not now. She needs to accompany us to the castle. Her absence would raise the enemy's suspicions, and the revelation that we know what we know would come too early."

languages.text: "Şimdi olmaz. Kaleye kadar bize eşlik etmesi gerekiyor. Yokluğu düşmanda şüphe uyandırır, neler bildiğimizi gereğinden erken öğrenmiş olurlar."
languages.original_text: "Not now. She needs to accompany us to the castle. Her absence would raise the enemy's suspicions, and the revelation that we know what we know would come too early."

languages.text: «Ahora no. Tiene que acompañarnos al castillo. Su ausencia levantaría las sospechas del enemigo y la revelación de que sabemos lo que sabemos llegaría demasiado pronto».

languages.text: “先不急，她得陪我们去城堡那边。要是她不在，肯定会引起敌人的怀疑，敌人也会意识到我们起了疑心。这件事情最好先别暴露。”
languages.original_text: "Not now. She needs to accompany us to the castle. Her absence would raise the enemy's suspicions, and the revelation that we know what we know would come too early."

languages.text: « Pas encore. Elle doit d'abord nous accompagner au château. Son absence éveillerait les soupçons de l'ennemi, et on s'apercevrait trop tôt que nous ne sommes pas dupes. »
languages.original_text: "Not now. She needs to accompany us to the castle. Her absence would raise the enemy's suspicions, and the revelation that we know what we know would come too early."

languages.text: "Nicht jetzt. Sie muss uns zur Burg begleiten. Ihr Fehlen würde das Misstrauen des Feindes wecken, wodurch dieser zu früh zu der Erkenntnis gelangen würde, dass wir wissen, was wir wissen."
